'''圣彼得堂'''（{{lang-en|St Peter's Church}}）是[[英格兰|英格兰]][[布萊頓和霍夫|布萊頓和霍夫]]的一部分，[[布萊頓|布萊頓]]中心的一座教堂。这是一座[[滑铁卢教堂|滑铁卢教堂]]，由竞赛获胜者，年仅二十余岁的年轻建筑师查尔斯·巴里爵士设计，建于1824年5月8日奠基<ref name="Harrison9">{{Harvnb|Harrison|1934|p=9.}}</ref>，当时是城市的入口，现在是市中心。1828年1月25日献堂。[[哥德復興式建築|哥特复兴建筑]]风格。1950年列为二级登录建筑<ref name="IoE481227">{{cite web|title=Detailed record: Church of St Peter (Brighton Parish Church), St Peter's Place, Brighton|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=481227&mode=quick|work=[[Images_of_England|Images of England]]|publisher=[[English_Heritage|English Heritage]]|year=2007|accessdate=14 January 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015051556/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=481227&mode=quick|archive-date=2014-10-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。从1873年到2007年，为布萊頓的牧区教堂，有时非正式地称为“布萊頓的主教座堂”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/4714001.Brighton_s_cathdral_welcomes_hundreds_to_reopening/ |title=Brighton's cathedral welcomes hundreds to reopening |accessdate=2014-10-09 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613084808/http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/4714001.Brighton_s_cathdral_welcomes_hundreds_to_reopening/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1978年，圣彼得堂与北街皇家礼拜堂合为一个牧区。<ref name="LG-47603-9085">{{London Gazette|issue=47603|date=28 July 1978|startpage=9085|accessdate=7 December 2012}}</ref>2007年12月，经过长期协商，教区牧灵委员会建议应裁撤圣彼得牧区<ref name="argus09022007">{{cite web|title=Two weeks to save church|url=http://archive.theargus.co.uk/2007/2/9/227283.html|accessdate=2008-02-06|publisher=Newsquest Media Group|date=2007-02-09|work=[[The_Argus_(Brighton)|The Argus]] website}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="stpclosure">{{cite web|title=December 2007 — Proposed Redundancy|url=http://www.stpeterschurchbrighton.org.uk/news.html|accessdate=2008-02-06|publisher=St Peter's Church Brighton|year=2007|work=St Peter's Church website|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060503054045/http://www.stpeterschurchbrighton.org.uk/news.html|archivedate=2006-05-03}}</ref>。2009年5月8日，伦敦的圣三一布朗普顿堂（Holy Trinity Brompton Church）同意接管其所有权。圣彼得牧区重组为一个单独的小牧区<ref name="argus07052009">{{cite web|title=Brighton's St Peter's Church saved|url=http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/4351210.Brighton_s_St_Peter_s_Church_saved/|accessdate=2009-05-08|publisher=Newsquest Media Group|date=2009-05-08|work=[[The_Argus_(Brighton)|The Argus]] website|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304032922/http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/4351210.Brighton_s_St_Peter_s_Church_saved/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

